data.description: Nestled in a charming quintessential Fredericksburg neighborhood, active STR "Haven Haus" is located on a corner lot just 6 blocks to historic Main Street! Vintage modern style flows throughout this updated and character filled 1950's 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with beautiful wood floors throughout. Attached sunroom leads to spacious backyard with beautiful mature trees and expansive patio. Large laundry room provides plenty of space to convert to third bathroom.  Thoughtfully decorated and furnished, this property comes truly turn key! Would also make a wonderful personal home!
